          <p class="info-text">Published in 1983, tends to give the lowest ideal weight estimates. Men: 56.2 + 1.41 kg per inch over 5 ft. Women: 53.1 + 1.36 kg per inch over 5 ft.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.1);color:#8b5cf6">
