          </div>
          <h3 class="info-title">Hamwi Formula</h3>
          <p class="info-text">Developed in 1964, one of the earliest IBW formulas. Men: 48 + 2.7 kg per inch over 5 ft. Women: 45.5 + 2.2 kg per inch over 5 ft.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
